data.description: Low maintenance and the neighborhood has a club house, a community pool, sidewalks and a park. Nice size backyard with shade trees.  The home boasts many custom upgrades including: plantation shutters, tile, granite countertops, custom wood cabinets, built-in cabinets, gas fireplace, screened in porch, rounded corners, arched doorways, smooth ceilings with recessed lighting, crown molding,  wood look  flooring throughout the home and carpet in the guest bedrooms.  Home has a formal dining room and large breakfast room, gated courtyard in the front of the home, irrigation system, gutters.  Enter your master suite through French doors, and you will find a large spacious bedroom with a beautiful tray ceiling and a bay window and beautiful custom ceiling details.  French doors lead to the backyard sun porch.  And the master bath has a double vanity, separate shower and jacuzzi tub, and a water closet, and you won’t want to miss the larger walk-in closet.  The home has a designated office with French doors and custom built-ins.  The screened in sunporch leads to a beautiful, large, shaded backyard.  Plenty of room to add a pool.  Enjoy a large laundry room with a sink and extra shelving.  The home is light and bright.  Hot water heater was replaced in April 2023.  Roof is one year old.  HVAC is one year old.  Side entry oversized 2 car garage. Beautiful courtyard entrance.
